WEBVTT

05:44.780 --> 05:45.910 line:80%
How many of you came?

05:46.880 --> 05:48.080 line:80%
Just Xie Qi and me.

05:48.340 --> 05:49.280 line:80%
We were afraid of being noticed,

05:49.280 --> 05:50.750 line:80%
so we didn't bring the other guards along.

05:50.750 --> 05:53.080 line:80%
Your Lordship, fortunately you are safe.
